tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE web_analytics (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    page_url VARCHAR(255),
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    activity_type VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE web_analytics (
  user_id INT,
  page_id INT,
  timestamp TIMESTAMP,
  action VARCHAR,
  PRIMARY KEY (user_id, page_id, timestamp)
);

CREATE TABLE personalized_content (
  user_id INT,
  content_id INT,
  personalized_text TEXT,
  timestamp TIMESTAMP,
  PRIMARY KEY (user_id, content_id)
);

CREATE TABLE web_analytics (
    user_id INT,
    page_id INT,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    event_type VARCHAR(255),
    PRIMARY KEY (user_id, page_id)
);

CREATE TABLE personalized_content (
    content_id INT,
    user_id INT,
    content TEXT,
    PRIMARY KEY (content_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (user_id) REFERENCES user_profiles(user_id)
);

CREATE TABLE web_analytics (
    user_id INT,
    page_id INT,
    visit_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    action VARCHAR(255),
    PRIMARY KEY(user_id, page_id, visit_timestamp)
);
